      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To accelerate locomotive fuel savings nationwide and provide incentives for owners of high polluting locomotives to replace such locomotives with newly-built or newly-remanufactured fuel efficient and less polluting locomotives.</title>
